commits.message: Added nojekyll flag.
Forgot to add docs to git.
Another attempt at fixing the deployment script.
Attempt to fix deployment.
Added build script and files to deploy.
Changed profile class to a card style.
Cards now fade in on initial load.
Added static resources from previous site.
Initial nuxt setup.
Added portfolio data from previous site.
Implemented profile.
Clean up page format and implement projects.
Added experience, project and education images.
Removed background from right pane.
Added media query to reformat page layout on smaller screens.
Added touch x,y swapping for touch screens with swapped touch coordinates.
Set default render mode in sample app to framebuffer.
Added engine options to invert touch x and y axis for inverted touch screens.
Reduced resolution to match sample hardware.
Fixed incorrect inversion calculation for x,y touch state.

Merge pull request #22 from lewpar/dev

Improve touch input on different touch hardware.

pull_request.title: Improve touch input on different touch hardware.
pull_request.body:
## Changes
- Added `InvertTouchX/Y` for inverting touch inputs.
- Added `SwapTouchXAndY` for touch screens that have swapped axis's.
- Added touch position to debug UI.
